env PAGER=cat man timing_enable_get_object_escaped_name_backward_c ompatible
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_enable...ard_compatible(25.10)    timing_enable...ard_compatible(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_get_object_escaped_name_backward_compatible

Syntax
       timing_enable_get_object_escaped_name_backward_compatible

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  printing  of  escape characters in the get_object_name command
       output.

       When set to false, the get_object_name command does  not  print  escape
       characters (starting with a backslash) in the object name.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

